short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Codesroom Screen Share extension is used to share screen on coderoom tutor panel

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Codesroom is the perfect place to learn a new programming language, or to practice your existing skills. It doesn't matter if you haven't wrote one single line of code in your entire life, Codesroom will help you become an expert. Codesroom offers a unique one 2 one support, where users will be taught online by a video conference.
